race.description: Hip Pocket Bendigo Spring Cup Final
race.comment: STACY'S MUM (1) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at Warrnambool but was a Grade 5 winner two back at Sale. Has the ability and can return to winning form this time. FLYING PROUD (2) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 2.5 lengths (34.35) at The Meadows. Rates a leading chance again. ASTON BARTON (8) has a strong record this trip including two wins from four starts. Comes off a (36.91) win last time, scoring by 8 lengths in a Grade 5 over 650m at Warrnambool. Can feature in the finish. MCIVOR ALFY (5) looks an each-way chance.

runners.name: Greysynd Sammy
